mksv3
The Free, Fast and Powerfull cross-platform text editor.
Python port and next generation of Monkey Studio v2

Home page:
    http://github.com/hlamer/mksv3
    http://monkeystudio.org
Documentation:
    http://hlamer.github.com/mksv3/
Home IRC room:
    #monkeystudio on irc.freenode.net
    
